reviewText:
A friend of mine gifted this game to me. It's so bad, it's actually really good!

Pros:
-Cheesy but hilarious dialogue;
-You can use the paintball gun and it deals plenty of damage;
-You can play as a skeleton;
-Your arms can regenerate when drinking water;
-Postal 2-like violence;
-Using green paint with the paintball gun can be useful for the Green Screen effect if you want to post an artwork;

